OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,FRussia is "relentlessly" targeting
OL,8,Fcritical infrastructure, democratic
OL,9,Fprocesses, supply chains and public
OL,10,Ftrust in the UK and Europe, the head
OL,11,Fof the UK's largest spy agency, GCHQ,
OL,12,Fwill warn.
OL,14,FAnne Keast-Butler is set to give the
OL,15,Finaugural GCHQ annual lecture on
OL,16,FWednesday, setting out how Russia is
OL,17,Fincreasing its daily hybrid activity
OL,18,Fagainst countries, including Britain,
OL,19,Fand how China is now a "science and
OL,20,Ftech superpower with sophisticated
OL,21,Fcapabilities".
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@XO]
