CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,FShe will urge the public and
OL,8,Fbusinesses to make cyber security "ten
OL,9,Ftimes more urgent".
OL,11,FThe speed of advancements in
OL,12,Ftechnology means there is a "narrowing
OL,13,Fwindow for the UK and allies to stay
OL,14,Fahead", she will say.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@pD@cOUqD@RO]vD@FO]
