OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,FShe is expected to highlight GCHQ's
OL,8,Fefforts in "disrupting Russia's
OL,9,Fefforts to smuggle western tech,
OL,10,Ffending off cyber attacks, and
OL,11,Fcountering reckless sabotage and
OL,12,Fassassination attempts", adding, "as
OL,13,Fwe remain steadfast in our support for
OL,14,FUkraine, Putin is going backwards on
OL,15,Fthe battlefield".
OL,26,@pD@LOUtD@WO]tD@bOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
