PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,FShe will urge the technology industry
OL,8,Fand those working in national security
OL,9,Fto "anticipate and drive advancements,
OL,10,Ftogether, at the speed of the
OL,11,Ffrontier", as well as calling on the
OL,12,Fpublic to take action "from boardrooms
OL,13,Fto living rooms" to increase cyber
OL,14,Fsecurity.
OL,26,@qD@DOUsD@IO]tD@WOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
