PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,F"At home, that means taking important
OL,8,Faction now to switch passwords for
OL,9,Fpasskeys, and for wider society, it
OL,10,Fmeans hardwiring security into new
OL,11,Ftechnologies, protecting supply chains
OL,12,Fand making cyber security 10 times
OL,13,Fmore urgent," she will say.
OL,15,FEarlier this year, Dr Richard Horne,
OL,16,Fhead of the National Cyber Security
OL,17,FCentre, which is part of GCHQ, warned
OL,18,Fthat most nationally significant cyber
OL,19,Fattacks on Britain were carried out by
OL,20,Fhostile states including China, Iran
OL,21,Fand Russia.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
