PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779916269
OL,3,CRussia 'relentlessly' targeting UK
OL,4,Cinfrastructure and democracy, warns
OL,5,CGCHQ boss
OL,7,FHe said the body dealt with around
OL,8,Ffour of these attacks each week, and
OL,9,Fwarned businesses to be prepared to
OL,10,Fprotect themselves against cyber
OL,11,Fattacks without needing the option of
OL,12,Fpaying ransoms, because the UK could
OL,13,Fbe targeted "at scale" if it were to
OL,14,Fbecome involved in an international
OL,15,Fconflict.
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@VO]
